text: Gema Pascual Torrecilla (born 12 January 1979) is a track and road cyclist from Spain. She represented her nation at the 2004 Summer Olympics in the Women's points race. ==References== ==External links== * profile at Cyclingarchives.com Category:1979 births Category:Spanish female cyclists Category:Living people Category:People from Madrid Category:Cyclists at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic cyclists of Spain
